撼到现在还记得，每重看一次都会有新的体会，但我明白京吹并不是一部百合番，甚至我觉得所有人际关系的描写都只是这部番的一个部分罢了，让我吹京吹，我肯定最先吹小黄的成长以及那段边跑边哭。虽然我与很多人一样希望高黄的关系能更进一步，但也不会因为作者没这样写就否定这部作品的价值。只能说它太优秀了，把不是它重点的部分也表现的太过深入人心。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"15172","username":"JustW","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"14880","dbdateline":"1561105496","groupiconid":"9"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":{"44217221":[],"44219587":[]},"commentcount":{"44217221":null,"44219587":null},"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"thread-{tid}-{page}-{prevpage}.html","group_group":"group-{fid}-{page}.html","home_space":"space-{user}-{value}.html","home_blog":"blog-{uid}-{blogid}.html","forum_archiver":"{action}-{value}.html","plugin":"{pluginid}-{module}.html"},"setting_rewritestatus":["portal_topic","portal_article","forum_forumdisplay","forum_viewthread","group_group","home_space","home_blog","forum_archiver","plugin"],"forum_threadpay":"","cache_custominfo_postno":["<sup>#</sup>","楼主",""],"forum":{"password":"0"}}}